text: George Damer (1727–1752), of Winterborne Came, Dorset, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of Great Britain for Dorchester 1751 to 1752. ==References== Category:1727 births Category:1752 deaths Category:Members of the Parliament of Great Britain for English constituencies Category:People from Dorset Category:British MPs 1747–1754
